different from a regular quad as it goes only 25km\/h and it keep you horizontal no matter what you&#x2019;re driving on. That way you can go off-road to all the most beautiful places in the Dordogne Valley. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13.jpg\" alt=\"sarlat france activities\"><\/noscript><img width=\"447\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sarlat france activities\" class=\"wp-image-61634 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-794x600.jpg 794w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-1072x810.jpg 1072w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-447x338.jpg 447w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-163x123.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-238x180.jpg 238w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-768x580.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-1024x774.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-1429x1080.jpg 1429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-1905x1440.jpg 1905w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161128\/sarlat-france13-300x227.jpg 300w, https:\/\/