\/sarlat-france33-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Opening hours:<\/strong> 9 AM &#x2013; 8 PM in the summer months. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.milandes.com\/en\/opening-hours-and-admission-rates\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Opening times differ during other seasons<\/a>.&#xA0;<br><strong>Entry fee:<\/strong> 12.50 EUR. This gives you access to the castle, gardens, and includes an audio guide.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/ile-de-re\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best things to do on Ile de Re!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161048\/sarlat-france9.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-61626 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161048\/sarlat-france9.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161048\/sarlat-france9-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161048\/sarlat-france9-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161048\/sarlat-france9-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07