-walnuts\">10. Try Truffle and Walnuts<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sarlat is famous for the truffle and walnuts found here! It&#x2019;s particularly well known for the elusive &#x2018;Perigord&#x2019;s Black Diamond truffle&#x2019; &#x2013; loved by Michelin star chefs from all over the world. To taste and buy, head to the famous truffle market in Sarlat.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> You can also visit the walnut museum to learn all about the process from harvesting to pressing. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"61630\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=61630\" class=\"wp-image-61630 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/19161108\/sarlat-france11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\